    com.hazelcast.nio.serialization.DataSerializable, IChildNet, NameTag, Network<TBus,TBranch>, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.InternalEObject
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    BaseAclfNetworkImpl, DcNetworkImpl, DistNetworkImpl

    public class NetworkImpl<TBus extends Bus,TBranch extends Branch>
extends NameTagImpl
implements Network<TBus,TBranch>
    An implementation of the model object 'work'.

    The following features are implemented:

    • Time Stamp
    • Base Kva
    • Frequency
    • Bus Number Arranged
    • Data Checked
    • Bypass Data Check
    • Allow Ground Branch
    • Original Data Format
    • Ref Bus Type
    • Ref Bus Id Set
    • Area Map
    • Zone Map
    • Owner Map
    • Substation Map
    • Branch List
    • Bus List
    • Tie Line List
    • Extra Info
    • Child Net Wrapper List
